{
  "stem": "13096.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And next to them, they had the pencils and the-- like a little stick, like a little pen with-- but it wasn't really very-- very painful.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they started putting, you know, like-- like a point-- they point at each number.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's got a point, you know, making the-- the-- the-- the alphabet-- first, the letter-- which group you belong.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Which mine, in that case, it was the A; and then after, making your number.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The number that I bear is 24283.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after, you know, they told us to keep the-- the-- the-- the arm outstretch until the ink will dry.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then the name-- the number, you know, will show very-- very strongly.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But myself, when they finish tattooing my arm, I went and I-- I rub it against my thing, because it-- I-- it was so ugly.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then today, it is one of the faintest number of all the other people-- they are from-- in my group.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everybody was scared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When they saw my-- my number like that, they say, be careful.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even the German girls, when they-- the-- the [NON-ENGLISH] told me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Be careful not to show to the Germans your number.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If they see it so fainted, they will kill you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because-- but I-- I didn't realize.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When you are young, you don't know what-- you know, you don't fear danger.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Anyhow, when the-- the-- the-- the thing was done, they took us, you know, to the-- to the blocks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was, you know, we-- they took us to the-- no.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I told you that they took us to be counted.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The-- the counting will be only-- will be only at 8 o'clock in the morning, with the German coming at 8 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
